===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}
{{wikipedia}}

# {{uncountable}} The chemical element (''symbol'' [[C]]) with an [[atomic number]] of 6.
# {{cattag|countable|informal}} A sheet of [[carbon paper]].
#: ''Make sure the '''carbon''' is facing the second sheet of paper, before rolling it into the typewriter.''
# {{cattag|countable|informal}} A [[carbon copy]].
# A fossil fuel that is made of impure carbon such as [[coal]] or [[charcoal]].
# {{cattag|ecology|uncountable}} [[carbon dioxide|Carbon dioxide]], in the context of [[global warming]] and [[climate change]].

